data.description: Introducing 27 Hedgegarth!  A hidden gem nestled in the heart of West Irondequoit, this 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom abode is the answer to your new home search.  Imagine coming home to relax by your wood-burning fireplace or enjoy your “me” time in the bright and airy sun porch!  The spacious two-car garage offers plenty of space for your vehicles or can be transformed into a hobby/workshop. The Kitchen is updated, the home also has hardwood floors, a charming brick front that adds a touch of timeless elegance to your home.  The vibrate I-Square neighborhood offers an array of amenities, all within walking distance, library, restaurants, shopping and more!  Don’t wait come see the value, convenience and comfort that 27 Hedgegarth has to offer.  Subject to the seller finding suitable property.
